			&lt;h4 align=\&quot;left\&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=\&quot;height_increase_line.php\&quot;&gt;HEIGHT INCREASE LINE | &lt;strong style=\&quot;color: #900;\&quot;&gt;Let’s see the model&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
			Our team is qualified in the production of shoes with height increase. By studying the design particularly, we are able to produce models of shoes with +7 and +10 centimeter of increase. The footwear seems to be normal externally. At the same time, thanks to the insertion of internal wedge, it enables the man to be taller in a comfortable way, stretching the body and supporting the posture and back in an invisible way.&lt;/div&gt;
