		&lt;div class=\&quot;extra-wrap2\&quot;&gt;
			&lt;h4 align=\&quot;left\&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=\&quot;orthopedic_line.php\&quot;&gt;ORTHOPEDIC LINE | &lt;strong style=\&quot;color: #900;\&quot;&gt;Let’s see the model&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
			Our orthopedic shoes are designed and made, in order to improve the deambulation and comfort of people. Suitable shoes (major volume) can be used in association to a customized orthotic. In the case in which the shoe has to be used to correct a specific pathology, its use has to be controlled by a specific doctor. Leathers are natural and not treated with prohibited substances. In addition, thanks also to the work of our artisans, the various elements of leathers are innovative and of the latest generation.
			&lt;ul&gt;
				&lt;li&gt;- The &lt;strong&gt;uppers&lt;/strong&gt; are realized through the use of soft leather or selfshaping elast nappa.&lt;/li&gt;
				&lt;li&gt;- The &lt;strong&gt;leather lining&lt;/strong&gt; can be padded on the forefoot in order to get the best breathability.&lt;/li&gt;
				&lt;li&gt;- Micro flexible &lt;strong&gt;Suole&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
				&lt;li&gt;- &lt;strong&gt;Increased volume&lt;/strong&gt; for the insertion of a customized orthopedic insole.&lt;/li&gt;
				&lt;li&gt;- &lt;strong&gt;Extractable orthopedic insole.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
				&lt;li&gt;- &lt;strong&gt;No friction of the internal lining seam.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;/ul&gt;
